    "lyrics": {
      "text": "Thou Who as God a-dorn--est and dost be-deck the sky__ with stars, and Who dost send forth Thine An--gels, through them, en-light-’ning all__ the earth, O Thou Cre-a-tor__ of all__ things, save them that hymn Thee__ with prais-es."
